description: THIS IS THE ONE YOU HAVE BEEN WAITING FOR !! Completely renovated 2BR/2BA penthouse condo on the East Side of South Boston. This brand new unit is just steps to the beach, Castle Island, and neighborhood favorites, The 1,300+ sq ft home features an open-concept layout connecting the kitchen, dining, and living areas perfect for entertaining or relaxing. The primary suite offers a private bath and walk-in closet; the second bedroom includes double closets and great natural light. Both bathrooms are fully updated. Highlights: private rear deck, in-unit laundry, central A/C, fireplace, and hardwood floors throughout. Prime location near MBTA bus lines to Broadway Station, Downtown, and the Seaport.
